<paragraph id="8BDF4C1F1351FFBD0841FA6AFD79F996" blockId="2.[264,1325,1188,1814]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<emphasis id="B914900D1351FFBD0841FA6AFDA1FA1E" bold="true" box="[312,610,1508,1534]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Collection information:</emphasis>
The 
<typeStatus id="54DBF2BD1351FFBD0BDEFA6AFCCDFA1E" box="[679,782,1508,1534]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">holotype</typeStatus>
and 
<typeStatus id="54DBF2BD1351FFBD0A28FA6AFC02FA1E" box="[849,961,1508,1534]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">paratypes</typeStatus>
from Jing­Fu­Shan mountain were collected in a bamboo forest by sweeping vegetation during the day. The forest is beside a small stream (width 
<quantity id="4C98E1FA1351FFBD0B24F9BAFD6AF9AE" box="[605,681,1588,1614]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" unit="m" value="1.5" valueMax="2.0" valueMin="1.0">1–2 m</quantity>
, water current less 
<quantity id="4C98E1FA1351FFBD0AF3F9BAFC7BF9AE" box="[906,952,1588,1614]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" unit="m" value="1.0">1 m</quantity>
/s, depth less than 
<quantity id="4C98E1FA1351FFBD0DF5F9BAFB21F9AE" box="[1164,1250,1588,1614]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" unit="mm" value="30.0">30 mm</quantity>
), with a substrate of small stone and leaves.
</paragraph>
